{"tid":626752,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"石棺藏屍案情 揭少女小草佔中時誤入歧途 案發時與三男同居","createTime":"2018-04-12T11:19:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T19:06:46.000Z","uid":73969,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"170c1c4bf412824ebf9b592c117965b2fdc0bef2","tid":626752,"uid":73969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T11:19:43.000Z","msg":"發生於前年3月荃灣工廈的石棺藏屍案今天在高院續審，控方傳召獲豁免起訴的證人，與三被告同住的少女「小草」何菱瑜作供。何作供前法官提醒她若作出虛假供詞或陳述，起訴豁免書會被視為無效。<br />\n<br />\n佔中結孽緣<br />\n控方在開案陳詞表示，何於佔旺行動中認識本案一眾被告，案發時雖有男友，仍與三被告同住在案發單位，並擔任首被告的秘書。次被告劉錫豪在被捕後向警方指稱，何與首被告關係是「契爺契女」。<br />\n<br />\n何稱案發當日聽到三名被告商量找地方殺人，但死者遇害時她雖然在單位內，但一直在閣樓睡覺，並無參與殺人，而事後首被告要求她別報警，何擔心男友安全故不敢報案。案件明天續審。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/silentmajorityhk/posts/1725256974230068\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsilentmajorityhk%2Fposts%2F1725256974230068&d=ASUwK%2Bpx0BiGpEbkl%2FvLzjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=9ffacb65\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/silentmajorityhk/posts/1725256974230068</a>"},{"pid":"f5b9c9194ac9e3f0f732f1f23570609d1b548598","tid":626752,"uid":39316,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T11:53:18.000Z","msg":"草含豐富葉綠素係好理所當然既事"},{"pid":"d307672d43a939620618d1c0e746ee7e73bb051f","tid":626752,"uid":73969,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T12:29:47.000Z","msg":"關佔中事是常識"},{"pid":"9d2fb7d3afe97c1e06623ff7468cbabc8c5721d2","tid":626752,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T12:46:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"836b27b521652cc096f6ad55f3e13c1db55d25b1","tid":626752,"uid":55924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T12:50:04.000Z","msg":"屈女士:又係佔中啦"},{"pid":"c05caf9cf900e2172790e2bee8845d32d681a42f","tid":626752,"uid":73969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T12:51:23.000Z","msg":"佔中又被講"},{"pid":"002b127191255e5047122c0a7765763371e12a3b","tid":626752,"uid":50595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T12:52:46.000Z","msg":"佔中趁熱鬧死mk"},{"pid":"2c484a29860283ccfd1b0169cc6c0d3bd4749641","tid":626752,"uid":73969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T17:37:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14c7457906e57b3d129865f67a0816cbf6109da4","tid":626752,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T18:21:11.000Z","msg":"唔好有事呀小草<br />\n支持你"},{"pid":"5fe0fdda980d980136d1bd7f8339c4e98b7f10e7","tid":626752,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T19:06:46.000Z","msg":"屌你老母又賴佔中，雞就雞"}]}